#. type: Title ====
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network-servers/_index.adoc:2505
#, no-wrap
msgid "Security Settings"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network-servers/_index.adoc:2509
msgid "The most important settings in [.filename]#/usr/local/etc/smb4.conf# are the security model and the backend password format.  These directives control the options:"
